1️⃣ Role – Tell the model who it is.
2️⃣ Task – Define exactly what needs to be done.
3️⃣ Context – Give constraints, preferences, and boundaries.
4️⃣ Reasoning – Explain how it should think before it answers.
5️⃣ Output – Control how the answer is delivered.
6️⃣ Conditions – Make it clear when the job is “done.”
